data.title: All Nobel Prizes in Literature
data.meta_description: All Nobel Prizes in Literature - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides summaries of the Nobel Prize in Literature from 1901 to 2014. It lists the 111 Nobel Laureates who have received the prize and provides a brief description of their works and reasons for receiving the award for most years. The 2015 prize had not been awarded yet at the time this document was written.
